---
title: API Gateway flow — Browser to backends
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser VERDANDI
    participant CH as Chur BFF
    participant KC as Keycloak
    participant SH as SHUTTLE GraphQL
    participant D as Dali
    participant M as MIMIR
    participant Y as YGG

    Note over B,Y: Login flow
    B->>CH: POST /auth/login
    CH->>KC: token grant_type=password
    KC-->>CH: access_token + scopes
    CH-->>B: Set-Cookie sid

    Note over B,Y: Read query (overview)
    B->>CH: POST /graphql query overview
    CH->>CH: lookup session
    CH->>SH: forward with X-Seer-User
    SH->>Y: Cypher read
    Y-->>SH: schemas
    SH-->>CH: response
    CH-->>B: response

    Note over B,Y: Mutation startParseSession
    B->>CH: mutation startParseSession
    CH->>CH: check scope seer:write
    CH->>SH: forward mutation
    SH->>D: POST /sessions
    Note over D: JobRunr.enqueue
    D-->>SH: Session QUEUED
    SH-->>CH: response
    CH-->>B: response

    Note over B,Y: MIMIR query
    B->>CH: mutation askMimir
    CH->>SH: forward
    SH->>M: POST /answer
    M->>M: tier 1 Claude
    M->>Y: tool call read
    Y-->>M: result
    M-->>SH: MimirAnswer
    SH-->>CH: response
    CH-->>B: response

    Note over B,Y: WebSocket subscription
    B->>CH: WS upgrade /graphql
    CH->>SH: WS upgrade forward
    SH->>B: connection established
    Note over B,SH: Events batched 50 per 100ms
